Axiom (addbubble):
  for all v0, (for all v1, (for all v2, (if v0 is an object and v1 is an object and v2 is an object then v0 + v1 + v2 is equal to v1 + v0 + v2)))

Axiom (addzero):
  for all v0, (if v0 is an object then (v0 + 0 is equal to v0 and v0 is equal to 0 + v0))

Axiom (addinvr):
